  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324210/extras/d42786127149fe8b39b7de2999c78a1f.avif?t=1728635642\" width=615 height=104 /></span><br><br>Stop Nemesis Prime as an Autobot or Decepticon.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324210/extras/5325716605ee164153457e369308dc00.poster.avif?t=1728635642\" width=600 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324210/extras/5325716605ee164153457e369308dc00.webm?t=1728635642\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324210/extras/5325716605ee164153457e369308dc00.mp4?t=1728635642\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Roll out for an intense fusion of arcade racing and robot combat in TRANSFORMERS: Galactic Trials! Evil NEMESIS PRIME has stolen the Prime Relics that bestow incredible powers on whoever possesses them. Now the AUTOBOTS and DECEPTICONS are in an explosive race to recover these powerful artifacts – which side will you fight for? <br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324210/extras/514b1ccdbeea967fd76b1afeae1b4c48.avif?t=1728635642\" width=615 height=104 /></span><br><br>Compete in a frenetic fusion of racing and combat.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324210/extras/460d5eab09034ac61a4cdf3ae5c112dd.poster.avif?t=1728635642\" width=600 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324210/extras/460d5eab09034ac61a4cdf3ae5c112dd.webm?t=1728635642\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324210/extras/460d5eab09034ac61a4cdf3ae5c112dd.mp4?t=1728635642\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Choose your character from icons like BUMBLEBEE, MEGATRON, and OPTIMUS PRIME, and speed into action on ten battle-race circuits. <br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324210/extras/b4aaa00efd086723ef16df81bf04d050.avif?t=1728635642\" width=615 height=104 /></span><br><br>Level up and customize 11 iconic Transformers.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324210/extras/30c9e4d93b5024c5c6d3b9b4faea51a9.poster.avif?t=1728635642\" width=600 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324210/extras/30c9e4d93b5024c5c6d3b9b4faea51a9.webm?t=1728635642\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324210/extras/30c9e4d93b5024c5c6d3b9b4faea51a9.mp4?t=1728635642\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Pull off sick drifts, charge your way through Boost Pads, and build up your Energon meter as you try to outpace your rivals.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324210/extras/7cb3421b3d7c3b69eb5e6fdc8a54e1e8.avif?t=1728635642\" width=615 height=104 /></span><br><br>Drift and boost around 10 action-packed tracks <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324210/extras/2f2d2376847757ba5cd671e3bcc0f327.poster.avif?t=1728635642\" width=600 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324210/extras/2f2d2376847757ba5cd671e3bcc0f327.webm?t=1728635642\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324210/extras/2f2d2376847757ba5cd671e3bcc0f327.mp4?t=1728635642\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Then convert into bot-mode and unleash devastating Energon-fueled skills, including OPTIMUS PRIME’s Energon Axe and BUMBLEBEE’s Plasma Sting, to fight your opponents to the finish line. As you gain experience and recover the powerful Prime Relics, you’ll build your skills and unlock new characters and skins. <br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324210/extras/b5958f4c34bfeb5c013af009d8390fbd.avif?t=1728635642\" width=615 height=104 /></span><br><br>Battle-race a friend in Versus mode.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324210/extras/ec800ccf942f6f9b5d394ac10cae8497.poster.avif?t=1728635642\" width=600 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324210/extras/ec800ccf942f6f9b5d394ac10cae8497.webm?t=1728635642\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324210/extras/ec800ccf942f6f9b5d394ac10cae8497.mp4?t=1728635642\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>This is more than a race and bigger than any battle. It’s the ultimate test of your favorite TRANSFORMERS’ robot abilities, which will decide the future of Cybertron!<br><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>CHOOSE YOUR SIDE –</strong> Stop Nemesis Prime as an Autobot or Decepticon <br></li><li><strong>BATTLE TO THE FINISH –</strong> Compete in a frenetic fusion of racing and combat  <br></li><li><strong>LEVEL YOUR CHARACTER –</strong> Level up and customize 11 iconic Transformers <br></li><li><strong>SPEED TO VICTORY –</strong> Drift and boost around 10 action-packed tracks <br></li><li><strong>LOCAL MULTIPLAYER –</strong> Battle-race a friend in Versus mode </li></ul>",
